{"tid":2094300,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】CLC莊錠欣Elkie潛水近三星期　更新IG曬螞蟻腰","createTime":"2020-07-04T13:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T18:52:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"886ccf95b4994c7fe159f64fb973f262e89f8b5e","tid":2094300,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"香港童星出身，韓國女團CLC成員莊錠欣Elkie不時在IG與粉絲互動，可是近期她潛水足足近三星期，粉絲都留言表示想念她。今天（4日）Elkie終於久違地更新IG，大曬一條Fit爆的螞蟻腰。<br />\n<br />\nElkie自上月14日上傳新相，慶祝好姐妹TWICE子瑜的21歲生日後就一直未有更新。雖然Elkie間中都有在限時動態回答粉絲問題，可是大家始終比較想看她的近照。今天Elkie終於久違近3星期，一次過上傳三張新相。穿上紫色露膊短上衣的她，大曬完美鎖骨及纖腰，而且更能隱約見到Elkie運動努力所得的11字腹肌。有粉絲留言大讚Elkie身形Fit爆，非常適合做牛仔褲Model！"},{"pid":"406ab6fa4771536ca3d1c05b0a177db3708ca7cc","tid":2094300,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200704/356084893706489856.jpeg/PedpZCmflcnVfj98WOyuqTeYroBrmA9Y_WAndP1gJ3Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200704%2F356084893706489856.jpeg%2FPedpZCmflcnVfj98WOyuqTeYroBrmA9Y_WAndP1gJ3Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7c28e2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200704/356086311406407680.jpeg/e01nmbtEu4nPPEVU46y062SHolrPrGRxw9lchMPZXIQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200704%2F356086311406407680.jpeg%2Fe01nmbtEu4nPPEVU46y062SHolrPrGRxw9lchMPZXIQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=53746444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200704/356086313667137536.jpeg/biM7YJyr6BH1-nsC_GVRU84SQ5B9-YjB9y_U8fcv1PE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200704%2F356086313667137536.jpeg%2FbiM7YJyr6BH1-nsC_GVRU84SQ5B9-YjB9y_U8fcv1PE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=17cf58b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89664d321eb065026ac642282b2a9d1d98fb5756",